data.title: Summer Camp 2024
data.text:
Athletic Summer Camps

Middle School Squash Camp

Week 3: July 29 - Aug 2

Week 4: Aug 5 - 9

Nardin Academy is excited to offer a series of squash camps for boys and girls entering 5th-8th grade. This camp is open to all skill levels and is run by Nardin Academy Squash Pro, Pamicka Marinello. Throughout the week, participants will be divided by level and will learn appropriate skills, techniques, rules, and gameplay.

Cost: $300

Time: 9 a.m. -12 p.m.

Location: Nardin Academy Athletic Center

Who can attend: grades 5th - 8th

Contact: Joe Baudo, jbaudo@nardin.org

*Please note, any requests for refunds must be made at least one week prior to the start of camp.
